### GET ALL BOOKS (with optional query)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book?query=
Accept: application/json

{}

### GET SINGLE BOOK BY ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/1
Accept: application/json

{}
### GET CUSTOMER INTEREST BOOKS
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/interest/1
Accept: application/json

{}

### GET BOOKS BY CATEGORY
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/category/1
Accept: application/json

{}

### GET BOOKS BY MULTIPLE IDs (POST with body)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/book/ids
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "ids": [1, 2, 4]
}

### GET LOW STOCK COUNT (assuming this endpoint exists)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/stock/low
Accept: application/json

### GET TOTAL BOOK COUNT (assuming this endpoint exists)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/count
Accept: application/json